ğŸ“Š Dashboard Metrics Explained

    Metric          Meaning
    ------          -------
    Total Users     Number of registered users
    Total Books     Number of books in catalog
    Active Issues   Books currently issued (not returned)

    Returned books are not removed from DB â€”
    only marked with return_date.


